Moreover, technological advancements in the field of catheter design and manufacturing are fueling the innovation and development of more advanced and user-friendly products. Manufacturers are investing in research and development to enhance the maneuverability, flexibility, and imaging capabilities of deflectable catheters, making them more efficient and effective for a wide range of medical procedures. These advancements are not only driving the adoption of deflectable catheters in traditional applications such as cardiology and urology but also opening up new opportunities in emerging medical fields.

